  <div class="ct">
  
<p>I have a poor relative I know deserves charity.. I also have some acquaintances I feel I should help. I donate directly to them, my largest donations. &nbsp;My small donations go to St Jude's Hospital, campaigns for Senator Bernie Sanders, Op-Ed News, American Society for Prevention of Cruelty to Animals, and several important political activist organizations. &nbsp;I never donate to anyone who telephones me to solicit, and I am always careful not to donate to organizations I do not know.</p>
